info.title: The First Cut Is The Deepest

lines.text: i would have given you all of my heart
but there's someone who's torn it apart
and she's taken just all that i have
but if you want to try to love again
baby, i try to love again, but i know
the first cut is the deepest
baby i know, the first cut is the deepest
and it come to bein' lucky she's cursed
when it come to lovin' me she's worst
